1. Open a post with related posts тАФ section should appear with minimal gap after the article body (only the 80px cv-body margin-bottom + border)
2. Each card shows: title (2-line clamp) тЖТ excerpt (1-line clamp, muted) тЖТ author + date
3. Cards without parseable content gracefully skip the excerpt line
